─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WHAT THIS TABLE IS
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

Unit of Measures is the canonical first table fully governed by the
execution layer architecture. It is a simple (non-child-scoped) table
with three operations: create, update, delete.

It was chosen as the first table deliberately:
- No ChildScopedRows, no async workflows, no outbox
- Smallest possible surface area
- Establishes the template all subsequent tables will follow

